Notice that $\omega _i^g(t) \geq 0$, thus $\tau_{0}  = \max \{ 0,\omega _i^g(t)\}  = \omega _i^g(t)$, and ${\Delta} = {\sigma _i} + \eta _{i,comm}^{g}(t) + \eta _{i,comp}^{g}(t)$.

